  "title": "Logistics Department Manager (Manufacturing Company)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- Hiring full time seafood processing logistic manager.</strong></p><p>- To work in factory located near Jurong Fishery Port.</p><p>- Midnight working hours (starts from 12 midnight till morning).</p><p>- Need to work on weekends and some public holidays.</p><p>- Candidates must be able to lead logistic team.</p><p>- Prefer Candidates with at least 2 years of experience managing logistic team</p><p>- Candidates must have at least class 3 driving licence.</p><p>- Prefer Candidates with at least 2 years of experience in planning of delivery schedule and route.</p><p>- Candidates are required to load and unload boxes of seafood from delivery lorries.</p>",
